Executor sabse pehle inputs uthata hai:-

applicationName = "Active Directory"
aggregationType = "Full / Delta"
checkDeleted = true
promoteAttributes = true
correlationRule = "MyRule"

👉 Ye aate hai:-
UI se
XML <Inputs> se

