✅ 6️⃣ Loop for EACH ACCOUNT 🔥:-
for each account:-
🔥 🔹 (a) ResourceObject kya hota hai?
ResourceObject account;
💡 Deep samajh:-
👉 Ye raw data container hota hai jo external system se aata hai,
External System → Connector → ResourceObject me aata hai.

🧠 Iske andar kya hota hai?
accountId / username  → unique id
attributes            → key-value data
Example:-
username = john.doe
email = john@gmail.com
department = IT
status = active

👉 Internally ye java me aise hota hai:-
account.getAttribute("email");
account.getAttribute("department");

🔥 🔹 (b) Correlation (DEEP 🔥)
💡 Goal:-
👉 Account ko correct Identity se match karna

🧠 Real Matching कैसे होता है?
✔ Default Matching:
account.email == identity.email
account.username == identity.name
account.employeeId == identity.employeeId

👉 Real me aur complex hota hai:-
domain check
multiple attribute mapping
fallback logic

✔ Identity mil gaya → OK
❌ Nahi mila → New identity create ho sakta hai.

🔥 🔹 (c) Identity Mapping (DEEP):-
👉 Correlation ke baad decide hota hai:-

✔ Case 1: Identity mil gaya toh,
Existing identity me update hoga attributes.
👉 Example:-
john@gmail.com already exist
→ same identity use hoga.

✔ Case 2: Identity nahi mila:-
New identity create ho sakta hai.
👉 Depends on config:-
Auto create ON → new identity banega
OFF → skip ya error

🔥 🔹 (d) Link Create / Update:-
🧠 Simple samajh
Identity ↔ Link ↔ Application Account
✔ Link me kya store hota hai?
applicationName  → AD / DB / etc
accountId        → john.doe
attributes       → email, dept, etc
🔥 Cases:-
✔ New account
Link create hoga
✔ Existing account
Link update hoga

🔥 🔹 (e) Attribute Sync / Promotion (DEEP):-
💡 Goal:-
👉 Account ke data ko Identity me update karna

🧠 Kaise hota hai?
account.email → identity.email
account.department → identity.department

🔥 Real me configurable hota hai:-
👉 XML ya UI se define hota hai:-
"email" → "email"
"dept" → "department"

🧠 Important:-
✔ Har attribute promote nahi hota,
✔ Sirf mapped attributes hi aate hai.
/////////////////*
🔥 ✅ 1️⃣ “Sirf mapped attributes promote hote hai” ka matlab
💡 Simple line
👉
Jo attributes map kiye gaye hai wahi account se identity me copy honge

🧠 Example se samajh:-
🔽 Account (external system se aaya):-
username = john.doe
email = john@gmail.com
department = IT
salary = 50000
location = India
🔽 Mapping config (IMPORTANT 🔥):-
email       → email
department  → department

👉 Notice:-
❌ salary mapped nahi hai
❌ location mapped nahi hai.
